Class Organizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • User
      • Organizer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<User>
    public class Organizer
extends User
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class contains the characteristics and actions of an organizer. They have the same characteristics as a user, except they have a list of events they will attend and a list of events they will organize.
    See Also:
